Caption: Prof. B. Sengupto and Mr. R. Natarajan (Foreground) standing at the microphones while the other dignitaries are seated at the dais
Description: On the dais sitting from left: Mr. M.C. Chagla, Dr. A.L. Mudaliar, xxx, Dr. Y. Nayudamma, Prof. Venkat Rao, Prof. Klein, Prof. P.C. Varghese and Prof. Lutz. Natarajan would proceed to retire from his post in the same month. His farewell party was held two days before the Second Convocation (1st April 1965). He officially retired on the 6th of April, after which Prof. C.V. Sethunathan took up the duties of the Registrar.
